## Summary
Verified and confirmed that Vercel Web Analytics is already properly integrated into the Art Things Brochure project following the official Vercel Web Analytics guide for Next.js App Router applications.

## Current Implementation Status

### ✅ Package Installation
- **Package**: `@vercel/analytics` version 1.3.1
- **Status**: Already installed in package.json dependencies
